    • Method Detail

      • convert

        public Map<String,Object> convert(TelephoneNumberType phoneNumber)
        This method creates a Map representation of the TelephoneNumberType provided. The following keys will be added to the map (Taken from EbrimConstants):

        COUNTRY_CODE = "countryCode"; PHONE_TYPE = "phoneType"; AREA_CODE = "areaCode"; NUMBER = "number"; EXTENSION = "extension";

        Parameters:
        phoneNumber - the TelephoneNumberType to be converted into a map, null returns empty Map
        Returns:
        Map representation of the TelephoneNumberType provided
